</p>
<p>Put a little <code>$battle = </code> in the beginning of all of this to get the new <code>Battle</code> object.
Perfect!</p>
<p>Now that the battle has been heroically fought, let's send back the gory details.
Use <code>return $this-&gt;createApiResponse()</code> and pass it <code>$battle</code> and the 201 status code:</p>
