</p>
<p>We aren't setting a <code>Location</code> header yet, so let's at least add a <code>todo</code> for that.</p>
<p>We are done! Controller, model and form: these are the <em>only</em> pieces we need to create
a robust endpoint. Try the test:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testPOSTCreateBattle</div></code></pre>
<p>We are in prime battling shape.</p>
<p>Now, let's complicate things and learn how to <em>really</em> take control of every field
in our endpoint. And, learn more about relations.</p>

    
